ZH: 请先把钱支付给我，其余金额可以在之后结算。
EN: Please pay me the money first, the remaining amount can be settled later.

ZH: 她会教我们第一课，其余的课程将由其他老师负责。
EN: She will teach us the first lesson, while the remaining classes will be taught by other teachers.

ZH: 在这家餐厅里，她点了一个汉堡，其余的则选择了披萨。
EN: In this restaurant, she ordered a burger while the rest chose pizza.

ZH: 请你把纸张都放在这个抽屉里，其余的办公用品可以放在那个柜子上。
EN: Please put all the paper in this drawer, and the rest of the office supplies can be placed on that cabinet.

ZH: 需要你认真完成这三个任务，而其余的则可以暂时搁置。
EN: You need to complete these three tasks carefully, while the rest can be temporarily put aside.

ZH: 他在比赛中获得了第一名，其余的选手都遥不可及。
EN: He won first place in the competition, while the rest of the participants were far behind.

ZH: 这个学校非常注重数学和科学，而其余的学科则不太被重视。
EN: This school places great emphasis on mathematics and science, while the rest of the subjects are not given much importance.

ZH: 请把这些文件整理好，其余的则可以丢弃。
EN: Please organize these documents properly, while the rest can be discarded.

ZH: 我打算用这笔钱购买新衣服，其余的留作存款。
EN: I plan to use this money to buy new clothes, while the rest will be saved.

ZH: 他赢得了注重的奖品，而其余的参与者都只是得到了鼓励。
EN: He won the coveted prize, while the rest of the participants only received encouragement.

ZH: 请把所有放在桌子上的物品收拾好，其余的则可以扔掉。
EN: Please tidy up all the items on the table, while the rest can be thrown away.

ZH: 他完成了大部分的工作，其余的细节需要与团队讨论。
EN: He completed most of the work, while the remaining details need to be discussed with the team.

ZH: 这个箱子里装着服装，其余的空间还可以放些其他物品。
EN: This box contains clothes, while the remaining space can be used for other items.

ZH: 客人们将会在会议室等候，而其余的人则需要在大厅里等待。
EN: The guests will wait in the conference room, while the rest of the people need to wait in the lobby.

ZH: 他们得到了优惠价格，而其余的购买者需要支付更高的费用。
EN: They got a discounted price, while the rest of the buyers need to pay higher fees.

ZH: 这篇论文包括了引言和结论，其余的内容则是详细的数据和分析。
EN: This paper includes an introduction and conclusions, while the rest of the content is detailed data and analysis.

