EN: Please divide these clothes into four piles, while the rest can be put in the storage box.

ZH: 这个菜单上列出了多种主菜，其余的则是饮料和甜点。
EN: This menu lists several main dishes, while the rest are beverages and desserts.

ZH: 他拿走了一部分书籍，其余的则留在图书馆里。
EN: He took some of the books, while the rest remained in the library.

ZH: 请将这些蔬菜放入冰箱，其余的则放在柜台上。
EN: Please put these vegetables in the fridge, while the rest can be placed on the counter.
